{"tid":512702,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"DIACLONE - FOSTER Team","createTime":"2017-12-28T18:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T17:24:12.000Z","uid":37125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68c07b0a7c08bd10dbbe1c29164333a71f030973","tid":512702,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T18:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/df06fec193e8fd7acb12528b7d2637e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fdf06fec193e8fd7acb12528b7d2637e0.jpg&h=d4f6d46a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">DIACLONE - FOSTER Team</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDiacloneFosterTeam&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokV0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b0595c0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DiacloneFosterTeam</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">依個 Facebook page 會以小弟自制嘅 Box Art 嚟講故事.<br />\n故事係關於 DIACLONE 入面一個叫 FOSTER 嘅小隊, 點樣喺X港以寡敵眾同幻亂誕軍團抗衡. 佢哋嘅目標就係將X港從幻亂誕帝國手中解放出嚟.</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於咩係 DIACLONE?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">DIACLONE 係 Takara 喺1980年推出去嘅約1/60嘅科幻戰爭玩具. DIACLONE 旗下嘅一條 line - Car-Robots, 就係而家大家所熟悉嘅 Transformers 變形金剛. 喺2015年, TakaraTomy 將 DIACLONE Reboot, 用舊有嘅 product 以更現代化, 更精細嘅 design 重新推出. <br />\n<br />\n經過重新 design 後, 新版 DIACLONE 系列入面每一個部件, 只要你諗到佢點用(玩), 就可以用自己嘅想像力, 想點砌就點砌. </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/big_poweredGV/img/bigpowred-gv_05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fbig_poweredGV%2Fimg%2Fbigpowred-gv_05.png&h=18297bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/big_poweredGV/img/bigpowred-gv_21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fbig_poweredGV%2Fimg%2Fbigpowred-gv_21.png&h=b2955dbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/big_poweredGV/img/bigpowred-gv_27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fbig_poweredGV%2Fimg%2Fbigpowred-gv_27.png&h=74fa543b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/big_poweredGV/img/bigpowred-gv_28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fbig_poweredGV%2Fimg%2Fbigpowred-gv_28.png&h=adda4697&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/product_details/img/pic_powerd-system.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fproduct_details%2Fimg%2Fpic_powerd-system.jpg&h=a0359ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/product_details/img/dia_nauts02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fproduct_details%2Fimg%2Fdia_nauts02.png&h=01a49a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/product_details/img/pic_powerdsuit_series02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2Fproduct_details%2Fimg%2Fpic_powerdsuit_series02.png&h=3f06908a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLNT-L4wvmY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeLNT-L4wvmY&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokV0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5adbbdf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eLNT-L4wvmY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lYOjNZI12uU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlYOjNZI12uU&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokV0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=717baccd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lYOjNZI12uU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOfficial site:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fproducts%2Fdiaclone%2F&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokV0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=da3bc51f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/</a><br />\n<br />\n依度有個 youtube playlist 玩具報告:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZ5yGT4Ans0&amp;list=PLVmVgo0o7T_8KlPLahG6wFwHbM3PMAje4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYZ5yGT4Ans0%26list%3DPLVmVgo0o7T_8KlPLahG6wFwHbM3PMAje4&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokV0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eba418b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZ5yGT4Ans0&amp;list=PLVmVgo0o7T_8KlPLahG6wFwHbM3PMAje4</a>"},{"pid":"7a8ea5842b6a1eac3d6dce78110043249080f047","tid":512702,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e0b053027a76a4650e7769ed7b724c4b4aaded","tid":512702,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04b59aa396a8c5b8845445859ca634a3da2ab66","tid":512702,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"係咪冇人知咩係 Diaclone? 我見兩登都冇咩人講."},{"pid":"61f630b147e1c1be943e2054636c45788738ab24","tid":512702,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.takaratomy.co.jp/products/diaclone/dia_battles_v2/img/pic_diabattles04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takaratomy.co.jp%2Fprodu